                      <pre about="#annotation-html-rdfa" property="schema:description" typeof="fabio:Script"><code>&lt;article about="#11a2cb4b-6814-4687-933d-8c25c917c746" id="20338295" typeof="oa:Annotation" prefix="rdf: http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns# schema: http://schema.org/ dcterms: http://purl.org/dc/terms/ oa: http://www.w3.org/ns/oa# as: https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams# ldp: http://www.w3.org/ns/ldp#"&gt;</code>
